snippet.title: Suicide Squad Insider Episode 2: Meet the Support Squad
snippet.description:
In episode 2 of Suicide Squad Insider, the team at Rocksteady gives the low down on our supporting cast and how they’ll give the Squad the tools they’ll need to take on the Justice League, as well as reveal some familiar returning faces.
!! STORY SPOILERS AFTER 7:34 !!

Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League is available 02-02-24 on PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC. 

Suicide Squad Game Latest News: https://studio.youtube.com/playlist/PLJms5sWamFOX_aaklmj-z9WFHgchG-qmq/videos
